{{Infobox book | name = Pastiches et mélanges | title_orig = | image = | caption = | author = [[Marcel Proust]] | country = [[French Third Republic|France]] | language = French | translator = | subject = | genre = [[Modernist literature|Modernist]] | publisher = | release_date = 1919 | english_release_date = | pages = }} '''''Pastiches et mélanges''''' is a 1919 collection of writings by [[Marcel Proust]].<ref>[http://www.gallimard.fr/Catalogue/GALLIMARD/L-Imaginaire/Pastiches-et-melanges Gallimard.fr]</ref><ref>[https://www.kb.nl/en/themes/koopman-collection/journees-de-lecture Kb.nl.en]</ref><ref>[http://www.edition-originale.com/en/literature/first-and-precious-books/proust-pastiches-et-melanges-1919-52809 Edition-originale.com]</ref>
